ndif]--&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;尽管霍尔木兹海峡仍然关闭，但随着买家与上个月的竞购狂潮发生&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/eUSf2pvRCIX1s6QUF2G787hUWofrh3L36Clk1k5HxZfyt2ODcdvnLUTUNdI0HGf2u7wr3XxEZKyMM76YfgNaM-56j2GiLusINr989hF2s9BtwL3zlMe8V8g-62zqoMWpSLtkB7Jl3p316uF-S9mfETshLsRpcdycsFIsJRc0an8nWJ5uEGrh9c21SA5fkfmV_8APkL4cKvzCetK_q_UsWhLMNA4lbud_EuL0olFoRqObX2czgCqbCevGtp8lpwB0_wxrrTT18cM5YnExpUndc1DXY2449GxF-40GSlnKhI5Ss6uvCY1Nj98U3yfwz1kMy_tyj28eUbPfuOTH_BQKMZMr6Tkxbnpr-_uZ5ppOataaiNfXSqH9hD71Gb7lIhhPWOdwF6D08dNkRJDcwkIGPudOakgpajnSnQgApzpbvQ7IhDkPp5hI8tVO4QkmcRq9S4oq2DiZGBWhEZAwVDNafRilDIrHuyJ6v8RSR0-_cHjOadhr9rLvPH8ibK-a9q8rQNGuFwcbQXOEMScpAKERkm9NbYO5N9ELtZ5s-w/8UALCSlel5XbkFcy3CsYCzssog7H2McF/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着买家撤离，实物石油紧缩状况暂时缓解"&gt;戏剧性逆转&lt;/a&gt;，现实世界石油货物的成本正在迅速下降。这次大幅回落为石油市场可能在几周内冲向危机点的警告提供了一个违反直觉的背景。尽管如此，交易员警告称，这种平静可能是短暂的。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;最后&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;由于缺乏资金和协调，欧盟正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/qWTFyeEGkaRVw2VtYBYP6WM1FjHa1DNleCUekH5AazjIXpq3Lmyr5yhCWCANrb-2iiZ4hlgGBa4QH884se_puIW7KhMxKzcwHiyTHG_aaw33AD9P2sE18LO-uIlSktaXmYv2dme93_JYnEpL2W_HyB3RYcm4EFPemwSlJxad4cVRcOq90FLo1NLKTtwvikeEQbmeWkSBBSX4ktc6dmMrklsYPc67bF_p_U2_Cmqau0njmzJ1PCJytoq5st1FdqvrOvhML4AyBTCmzgjkxa3aXD9RsDHYJG3Y49f-ahnLN1cShYf2pCFGJJ4S8J3mMqxRBo4g6CEOMaHD6OEss29FXayu-6ytTuzNbH8Z4ZnJkEo0VGxkEAfCoihIGffV082RmVwj8Q-8ZgEDNgVl6wC6_Cb8m1TTryBnwfSfBZf5q5T-mdqYWhOdik5bwejDvU35emk4xdxDVbTCRfWimOVWI2SQv1LNh9mzbFwLQcPwbgLbFnvECz33UG7w7EzyauC03OQFfgIQpp9CuNm-AQ5G6HNOyj5nwv-7aTma7Q_V/J38xhm-sOQSLNjWya-Yzftdk12OqCzZZ/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="关键矿产的争夺使欧盟难以跟上"&gt;努力确保获得&lt;/a&gt;用于军事装备的锑等关键矿物。斯洛伐克的 Trojarova 项目由加拿大军事金属公司 (Military 